We release a large dataset as a resource for further research: Up to\footnote{For some concepts, the final candidate set contains less than 1k candidates due to lack of enough siblings' positives and/or deletion during scrutiny steps} top-1k negations for all primary concepts from Ascent [ascentpp], containing 6.2m negations\footnote{\url{https://www.mpi-inf.mpg.de/departments/databases-and-information-systems/research/yago-naga/commonsense/uncommonsense}}.